==English==

===Noun===

'''trace fossil''' (''plural'' [[trace fossils]])

# A type of [[fossil]] reflecting the reworking of [[sediment]]s and hard [[substrate]]s by organisms, rather than the physical remains of the organism itself. This includes structures such as [[burrow]]s, [[trail]]s, [[impression]]s, [[coprolite]]s and [[boring]]s.

